data.description: Home sweet home! Nestled in a quality family-oriented neighborhood with an elementary, Jr high, and private school located within the block. Rainbow Falls water park, high school, baseball field, skate park, and playground within 5 min walking distance. Lowest property taxes in alll of cook county and near Alexian Bros hospital. This home is conviently located in-between highways 355/ 290 / 53/ 90.    Kitchen features stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, metal backsplash, and hand scraped porcelain tile "chocolate" floors. All bathrooms have been renovated. Main living spaces updated with gray wood vinyl plank flooring and recessed led lighting throughout the home with dimmers. Roof 2020 under warranty, crawl space is climate controlled and "perma" sealed for additional storage. Newer and higher efficiency mechanicals including furnace. Garage is 2.5 car and is used as a one-car with 1.5 as storage and a workspace, door is new 2021 insulated and warranted. Home security system included.
